KONVERT

This is a small utility to download youtube videos by emulating a 
browser on www.online-convert.com


konvert -a <youtube-url-here>
    This will enqueue download (on video.online-convert.com). Target
    format - MP4

konvert -c
    This will check for status of all previously enqueued downloads,
    and download the MP4, if the server is ready to serve.

konvert -C <username>
    To enqueue videos (for download) uploaded by the given user.

konvert -p <path to download video(s)>
    Directory of the videos where to download. Default Users download
    directoy.
